title: Unleashing the flight of the Jungling Quinn

embed.description: Doing some solo q jungle trolling qith Quinn and Valor. She actually works damn well and has a fair crack of shut down with that silence on her q. You can also find on twitter @ https://twitter.com/shaunofdasheep And credit for the soundtrack goes to https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oj6X_xqZ4Ws Anyway, enjoy and don't forget to like and subscribe.

body: Tried out jungle quinn.  I'd say maybe viable, not really great for ranked in higher tier though haha

replies.body: But in the end, she is actually holding the highest win rate in plat and above... lmao. Bird jungle - who would have thought.
